---
title: Mexican-Spiced Chicken with Charred Pineapple Salsa & Mixed Greens Salad
description: Mild-tasting pork loves a little something sweet, which we think pairs beautifully with spicy heat. Lucky you, tonight’s dinner has it all! Succulent pork tenderloin is seared with our Mexican Spice Blend, roasted to perfection, and topped with an amazing charred pineapple and jalapeño salsa. We pile on more fresh flavor with tender greens dressed in a creamy spice-kissed dressing. Cheers to perfect pairings!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/632b30a8ea7642fab4003f1f-ba0d4181.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/mexican-spiced-chicken-632b30a8ea7642fab4003f1f-2d363d4f.pdf
